Title: What Will Happen to the Gang Next Year?
Plot: Determined to prove his marriage has survived Avery's kidnapping unscathed, Jack asks Liz to officiate their vow renewal. Meanwhile, Criss (Marsden) tries to convince Liz that he's worth sticking around for. Tracy meets with Cornel West to discuss his influence as a black celebrity.
GuestStars: James Marsden, Mary Steenburgen, Margaret Cho, Kristen Schaal, Michael Mosley, Thomas Roberts, Cornel West, Pat Kiernan, Elizabeth Banks
